      <abstract>
        <p>Deportation from Hungary to Ukraine in 1942. Author’s return to Hungary. Stay in the
          ghetto of Nagyszollos. Deportation to Auschwitz. The author with his twin brother served
          as guinea-pigs for medical experiments there.</p>
      </abstract>
